          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1701944472992-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>hake fillet[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper and chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped hake </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper </strong>(can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix until the hake is evenly coated – this is your <strong>coated hake</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1701944480389-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1701944480389-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1701944480389-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1701944480389-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1701944480389-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated hake</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until cooked through – this is your <strong>smoky hake</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1701944487648-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1701944487648-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1701944487648-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1701944487648-x1000.jpg",
